d0b636e3-7f7a-4694-aded-041a60c2c102.title: Gamfred
d0b636e3-7f7a-4694-aded-041a60c2c102.text:
Ello there. I'm Gamfred, the engineer in this here guild.
Have you seen my catapult?

options.text: That's not a catapult, it's a large crossbow.
May I claim my tokens please?

96fae878-8e76-4929-9d70-9fffa30136f5.title: <player>
96fae878-8e76-4929-9d70-9fffa30136f5.text: That's not a catapult, it's a large crossbow.

8b1fca56-8e41-4b0a-861b-5ad066b08cd7.title: Gamfred
8b1fca56-8e41-4b0a-861b-5ad066b08cd7.text:
WHAT!? I'll have you know that is the finest piece of
dwarven engineering for miles around! How DARE
you insult my work!

3b81f062-d553-46db-9169-587110a5190b.title: Gamfred
3b81f062-d553-46db-9169-587110a5190b.text:
Nice to meet someone who appreciates fine work, have
you tried it out yet?

options.text: No, how do I do that?

7e49b421-afb8-4a7b-b839-345ed9a7ecaa.title: <player>
7e49b421-afb8-4a7b-b839-345ed9a7ecaa.text: No, how do I do that?

adf2b2ca-e650-411a-bbbe-1f3e2d37788f.title: Gamfred
adf2b2ca-e650-411a-bbbe-1f3e2d37788f.text:
Well ye take the big defence shield in both hands and
watch the catapult. My assistant will fire different things
at you and you need to defend against them.

options.text: May I have a shield please?

3bf228cd-3f1b-4d27-a40c-ced0521086ca.title: Gamfred
3bf228cd-3f1b-4d27-a40c-ced0521086ca.text:
Are ye blind? Tis over there in the next room with
me assistant working it!

81fc2618-a1bd-454a-b783-063f4178343e.title: Gamfred
81fc2618-a1bd-454a-b783-063f4178343e.text: Come back soon! My catapult needs more test subjects.

5dbf11bb-25b4-46c1-896b-f857ab2bcb5c.title: <player>
5dbf11bb-25b4-46c1-896b-f857ab2bcb5c.text: May I claim my tokens please?

69cc24c4-ac97-4eaf-a282-f05e30f079b2.title: Gamfred
69cc24c4-ac97-4eaf-a282-f05e30f079b2.text:
I'm afraid you have not earned any tokens yet. Try
some of the activities around the guild to earn some.

50ca5399-19bc-41ce-89c6-ebbb7e93093d.title: <player>
50ca5399-19bc-41ce-89c6-ebbb7e93093d.text: Ok, I'll go see what I can find.

options.text: May I have a shield please?

e485b2cb-e352-4baf-ab90-fc30d8f0442a.title: Gamfred
e485b2cb-e352-4baf-ab90-fc30d8f0442a.text: Well I guess not everyone will like it.

1df60725-d33e-424a-ab02-22b44e809abb.title: Gamfred
1df60725-d33e-424a-ab02-22b44e809abb.text:
Glad ta hear it. Try it again sometime. We have more
tests to run.

79e14964-8acc-4186-be94-a6657493af3e.title: Gamfred
79e14964-8acc-4186-be94-a6657493af3e.text:
Well I guess not everyone will like it. But give it
another chance before you go.

90a925ed-aa6c-4472-8489-fba8d4e7c36d.title: <player>
90a925ed-aa6c-4472-8489-fba8d4e7c36d.text: May I have a shield please?

1e2f01f9-621e-4699-ae89-6864a9866349.title: Gamfred
1e2f01f9-621e-4699-ae89-6864a9866349.text: Silly muffin, you have one already!

aee636bb-0bc6-4a9a-a4ac-69aa987dec97.text: The dwarf hands you a large shield.
